TopicTitle: I have the fuel line twice

Articles.Content:
the fuel line appears twice in the fuel tanks tab in the editor.

Is this meant to happen?

0.90 completely redid the strut/fuel line code and relocated their assets. If you used the patcher to update, then your old ones have not been deleted. You can either delete the Squad folder and rerun the patcher or you can delete the strutconnector and fuelline folders manually. The former is in structural and the latter is un utility.
